title: E150 THE SADDEST MOMENT IN IMPAULSIVE HISTORY - IMPAULSIVE EP. 150

description:
Before Spencer drops a very sad atomic bomb DURING the podcast, the boys reveal what it takes to make their “blacklist,” why Logan refuses to acknowledge birthdays, Antonio Brown’s REAL reason he denied the first fight offer, how Kevin Hart’s documentary may have hurt his reputation, and the return of the Vlogs.
